node.text: As an entrepreneur, do you struggle going on vacations..? If so, this message is for you! I made this video a few years ago, but thought it was appropriate to post, now that we’re half way through the summer… in hopes to remind you that you’re not weird… you’re an Entrepreneur, and that’s ok!!

node.text:
The last 12 months have been hard for many…

But for those who were at FHL, we were prepared… One month before the lockdown, we had 5,000 ‘Funnel Hackers’ together at FHL, and @TonyRobbins predicted what was about to happen…

We just released an “After Movie” from FHL 2020, and it INSTANTLY gets me back in state to continue to create… to work… to serve!!! I can only hope it does the same for you :)

node.text: How she changed her life by launching an ebook telling her most vulnerable story...

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Russell Brunson on July 23, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of 1 person and text that says 'Russell Brunson @russellbrunson 208-231-3797 ㅇㅇ° What funnels are you building this weekend?'.

node.text:
The weekend isn’t just a time for rest... it’s a time to get ahead!!!

So let’s hear it!!! What Funnels are you working on this weekend?! Drop your answer in the comments below 👇

People will throw stones at you, but it’s up to you to decide what to do with them…

You could throw them back, and feed into the negativity, or you could use them to build something bigger... ;)

I’ll always choose to build something bigger with what’s thrown at me :) What about you?

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Russell Brunson on July 21, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of 1 person and text that says 'Russell Brunson @russellbrunson 208-231-3797 ㅇㅇ° There are 4 types of wealth: 1. Financial wealth (money) 2. Social wealth (status) 3. Time wealth (freedom) 4. Physical wealth (health)'.

node.text:
Your time and health are priceless…

We only have one life to live on this earth… so stop chasing things that won’t matter in the end!!!

The work we do to accomplish our mission in life is vital, but having the time and health to be able to fulfill that mission is what makes it all possible! So make sure you aren’t selling yourself short and being robbed of them!!!

I’m curious to know… what type of wealth do you wish to have more of right now? Leave your answer in the comments below!!!

node.text:
This one is for all my fellow introverts out there… :)

I want you to know how possible it is to succeed in what seems like an extrovert’s world!

It’s going to be hard and you’re going to suck at first, and that’s okay…we all do! But the more you put your message out there, the better you become…

Because at the end of the day, the only thing that truly matters is the impact you have on people’s lives, so stick to it… it’s worth it :)

#introvert #focusonyou #happiness #extrovert #obsessed #perspective #faith #opportunity #lifetime #successtips #businesstips #goalgetters #buildingmybrand #successfulmindset #entrepreneurmotivation #greatideas #agreeable #takeaction #nevergiveup #motivationalspeech #businesspassion #marketingcampaign #themomentisnow #love #stayfocused #bepositive #overdeliver #russellbrunson

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Russell Brunson on July 19, 2021 tagging @russellbrunson. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'DEANGRAZIOS RAZIOSI BEAN TRAFFIC SECRETS IE RUSSELL S BRUNSON Russell Brunson @russellbrunson 208-231-3797 208 231 3797 All of the missed parties, being criticized and misunderstood, the late nights and early mornings... it'll all pay off... Keep going!'.

node.text:
I promise you everything is going to be worth it…

The missed parties, being misunderstood and criticized, staying up late and waking up early… all of your hard work and effort, it’s all going to pay off! You just have to KEEP GOING!!!

You’re not doing all of this for nothing… you have a reason, a purpose, a mission, and it’s your job to keep pushing through no matter what. I promise it’s going to be worth it :)

Who’s with me on this?! Let me know!!!

node.text: As an entrepreneur, do you struggle going on vacations..? If so, this message is for you! I made this video a few years ago, but thought it was appropriate to post, now that we’re half way through the summer… in hopes to remind you that you’re not weird… you’re an Entrepreneur, and that’s ok!!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Russell Brunson on July 16, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Russell Brunson @russellbrunson 208-231-3797 ㅇㅇㅇ You are not lazy, unmotivated, or stuck. After years of living your life in survival mode... are exhausted. There's a difference.'.

node.text:
We’re all on our own journey’s, doing our best to get closer towards our goals…but I think a lot of us can beat ourselves up too much when times get hard…

It’s so important to understand the difference of feeling unmotivated or stuck, and simply being exhausted from giving your all so consistently… because this game isn’t easy!!!

Learn when it’s time to step back and regain your focus, understand the direction you’re going, remember why you started, and get back at it!!! That’s what makes the difference :)

Drop a “❤️” if you agree!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Russell Brunson on July 15, 2021 tagging @russellbrunson. May be an image of 2 people and text that says 'Russell Brunson @russellbrunson 208-231-3797 Remember, almost everything in life can be solved with good be marketing.'.

node.text:
Almost every problem in life can be fixed with good marketing. I don’t care what it is. You give me a problem in your business, or your life, and it boils down to this: You’re bad at marketing!

Remember that as you go on in your journey… almost everything in life can be solved with good marketing ;)

Who’s with me?

node.text:
THIS is what you need to do to change lives :)

So grateful and blessed for these experiences working with the @villageimpact team in Kenya…

Witnessing the amazing work these local leaders are doing really opened my eyes and helped me serve people on a whole new level. Such an important reminder that education is the best gift anyone can give to have a lasting impact :)

So I hope this lesson helps you as much as it did me... education is the key to changing lives forever, never forget that!!!

node.text:
If you want to be successful in life, you need to MAKE and KEEP your commitments…

To yourself…
To the people you love and care about…
To the people you work with…
And to the people you serve.

So stop letting yourself off the hook…because your commitments are everything!!! So always remember them and KEEP THEM.

Comment 💯 if you agree!!!

node.text:
Entrepreneurs are the only people that can actually change the world :)

They are the ones that will sacrifice everything they have to get their message out there… because they believe in it and they know it will impact people’s lives….

Looking back at everything amazing that has happened in my life… I’ve realized it’s all because there’s an entrepreneur out there who sacrificed what they had for what they believed in :)

So entrepreneurs, I know you guys are sacrificing for your mission… and just know that you ARE changing the world in your own way :) Don’t give up, because your people’s need you more than you could ever know…

node.text: Lake Powell 2021 is in the books! We wake surfed, flyboarded, wake boarded, skied, knee boarded, foiled, and e-foiled… and had an amazing time with family and friends.  What are you doing for your summer vacation this year? Let me know if the comments below!!
